  "detailed_description": "Many abandoned houses are full of ghosts. These can be the souls of suicides or demons. It could be the spirit of a vampire, slowly sucking the blood from everyone who comes near<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850740/extras/eb0b61380b2e6461f90ba3acb274f809.avif?t=1763218794\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br><br><strong>ADVANTAGES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20 types of unique ghosts - the souls of people and strange creatures, as well as several types of demons<br></li><li>Each ghost has its own unique attack and animations<br></li><li>Over 60 types of detailed tools for collecting evidence and fighting ghosts<br></li><li>You can determine the type of ghost, its age and mood<br></li><li>7 game locations filled not only with clues to catch ghosts, but also with interesting Easter eggs<br></li><li>Different types of game modifiers, they help diversify the gameplay</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850740/extras/bd23150be45cc51635accd6cc5fadd17.poster.avif?t=1763218794\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850740/extras/bd23150be45cc51635accd6cc5fadd17.webm?t=1763218794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850740/extras/bd23150be45cc51635accd6cc5fadd17.mp4?t=1763218794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br><br>You will have to explore the ghost, and then catch it! In this hunt everything is important: look for evidence, find out the age of the ghost, feel what kind of mood it is in<br><br><strong>EARLY ACCESS</strong><br><br>We will be adding new ghosts and new locations to the game",
  "about_the_game": "Many abandoned houses are full of ghosts. These can be the souls of suicides or demons. It could be the spirit of a vampire, slowly sucking the blood from everyone who comes near<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850740/extras/eb0b61380b2e6461f90ba3acb274f809.avif?t=1763218794\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br><br><strong>ADVANTAGES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20 types of unique ghosts - the souls of people and strange creatures, as well as several types of demons<br></li><li>Each ghost has its own unique attack and animations<br></li><li>Over 60 types of detailed tools for collecting evidence and fighting ghosts<br></li><li>You can determine the type of ghost, its age and mood<br></li><li>7 game locations filled not only with clues to catch ghosts, but also with interesting Easter eggs<br></li><li>Different types of game modifiers, they help diversify the gameplay</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850740/extras/bd23150be45cc51635accd6cc5fadd17.poster.avif?t=1763218794\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850740/extras/bd23150be45cc51635accd6cc5fadd17.webm?t=1763218794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850740/extras/bd23150be45cc51635accd6cc5fadd17.mp4?t=1763218794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br><br>You will have to explore the ghost, and then catch it! In this hunt everything is important: look for evidence, find out the age of the ghost, feel what kind of mood it is in<br><br><strong>EARLY ACCESS</strong><br><br>We will be adding new ghosts and new locations to the game",
